      "fix": "Preprocess prefix sums for both sorted arrays. For each query k, compute the number of b‑items that can replace a‑items using binary search: find the largest index p such that a[i] + k ≥ b[p] for each a[i]. The total sum can then be calculated as sum of the chosen a‑items plus sum of the chosen b‑items using the prefix sums, all in O(log n) per query.",
